# Directions to L100 Draining Trainer (Quintard, mob 6791)

say { "Hello";
	say Hello stranger, what brings you here this day?;
	}

say { "trainer";
	tell %n Finding your trainer is part of your growth;
	tell %n However, I can give you a hint....;
	tell %n Hot and dry is the place you seek,;
	tell %n where brigands spend hour-less feats.;
	tell %n South bound Grimhaven then turn East,;
	tell %n Venture off the path and you'll be in a heap!;
	cackle;
	}

